[gd_scene load_steps=124 format=3]

; SNOW — Sprawling winter realm for a ~1.5m penguin.
; Major landmarks (south to north, roughly):
;   - Arrival Clearing w/ signpost + snowdrift border
;   - Snowy Village: 5 CSG cabins (general store, tavern w/ bar+stools,
;     forge, two homes), village well, hanging lanterns, bark fences
;   - Snowman Family (3 sizes)
;   - Pine Forest winding path (20+ conifers w/ stacked cones)
;   - Frozen River w/ cracked ice strips + stuck boat
;   - Chairlift System (3 towers, cable + cable-car box midspan)
;   - Mid-mountain Ski Lodge (multi-room: main hall, fireplace,
;     tables, booths, upstairs loft, back storage with skis)
;   - Frozen Waterfall + Ice Cave (CSG tunnel → carved chamber
;     w/ crystals, frozen sub-lake, hidden 1up shrine)
;   - Igloo Village (3 domes, one walk-in w/ fur bed + fire)
;   - Ski Slope slalom return (very_slippery w/ red flags)
;   - Mountain Peak Weather Station (observatory dome, radar, antenna)
;   - Frozen Pond Plaza (reflection, metal cap at center)
; Content: 18 enemies, 45 yellow + 8 red coins, 3 stars, 4 1ups, 1 metal cap.

